issue_series_s: Sixth War Issue Bills of Credit
issue_place_s: Woodbridge, New Jersey, United States of America
issue_obverse_legend_s: THIRTY SHILLINGS. | THIS BILL by LAW shall pass current in NEW-JERSEY, for Four Ounces, Seven Penny-weight, and Twelve Grains of SILVER. June 14, 1757. Thirty Shillings.
issue_reverse_legend_s: Thirty Shillings. | To counterfeit this Bill is DEATH. | Woodbridge, in New-Jersey: | Printed by James Parker.
